WEBVTT

00:00:00.440 --> 00:00:02.420
I want to die anyway.

00:00:02.640 --> 00:00:04.420
We die together.

00:00:06.280 --> 00:00:09.780
The martial arts world will die with me.

00:00:10.360 --> 00:00:11.940
Worth it.

00:00:12.640 --> 00:00:13.720
I cannot die.

00:00:13.720 --> 00:00:14.940
I cannot die.

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:17.300
I am not the leader yet.

00:00:20.760 --> 00:00:22.100
Do it again next life.

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:24.100
Pham Hien, what's wrong with you?

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:26.540
I have nothing.

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:27.720
Let's go.

00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:29.940
Come on, we'll get married when we get home.

00:00:43.320 --> 00:00:44.420
I'm not dead.

00:00:49.960 --> 00:00:51.260
Pham Hien, don't.

00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:52.420
Don't do that.

00:00:52.480 --> 00:00:54.140
Their deaths have nothing to do with you.

00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:56.380
And your immortality will now never be complete.

00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:59.500
If you share your life with others, you will not live.

00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:00.660
For whatever reason.

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:02.420
They died for me.

00:01:03.080 --> 00:01:04.100
Revenge.

00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:05.620
It is also necessary to let go of some resentment.

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:07.540
When to report injustice?

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:09.860
Sister Chu, please stop this backlash.

00:01:09.880 --> 00:01:12.220
If he saves people like that, he won't live long.

00:01:12.240 --> 00:01:13.420
I don't want you to die.

00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:16.220
If you die, I will die with you.

00:01:16.280 --> 00:01:17.500
Actually I understand.

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:19.580
Immortality is not important.

00:01:19.640 --> 00:01:21.860
It matters who you spend time with.

00:01:22.040 --> 00:01:24.140
If the future days don't have you coming

00:01:24.240 --> 00:01:25.500
I can't accept.

00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:27.220
So we can practice together.

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:29.180
The feeling of immortality increases over time

00:01:29.320 --> 00:01:31.300
Will take away the seven emotions and six desires of man.

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:34.540
This is what I felt after finishing the practice except for the sixth level.

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:36.060
So...

00:01:36.920 --> 00:01:37.980
No more practice.

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:40.620
It was his choice.

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:42.340
Just let him do it.